T1  - Optimal capital structure: A multi-period programming model for use in financial planning
AU  - Brick, Ivan E.
AU  - Mellon, W.G.
AU  - Surkis, Julius
AU  - Mohl, Murray
JO  - Journal of Banking & Finance
VL  - 7
